verbose_text: The expression levels of IL-1beta, IL-6, IL-17, TNF-alpha, TGF-beta, and alpha-SMA (as a myofibroblast marker) were all decreased by anakinra treatment, which suggested anti-inflammatory and antifibrotic effects of the IL-1Ra in this BLM induced fibrosis model.
evidence: levels of IL-1beta, IL-6, IL-17, TNF-alpha, TGF-beta
